    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Morphological characters. (A, B) head, frontolateral: (A) Zagrammosoma multilineatum, (B) Cirrospilus sp. D3751. (C) hind leg: Zagrammosoma trifurcatum n. sp. (D–G) mesosoma, dorsal: (D) Cirrospilus sp. D5964, (E) Zagrammosoma calvini n. sp., (F) Zagrammosoma americanum, (G) Burkseus singa. (H) fore wing: Zagrammosoma lineaticeps. (I) head and antennae, lateral: Zagrammosoma trifurcatum. Scale bar = 0.2 mm (A–G, I), 0.5 mm (H). Abbreviations in text." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4471807/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

